column2: SELECT ts.SystemStudentID StudentID FROM Enrollment e INNER JOIN TestScores ts ON e.SystemStudentID = ts.SystemStudentID INNER JOIN ParentEngagement pe ON pe.StudentID = ts.SystemStudentID INNER JOIN EmotionalScreener es ON es.StudentID = pe.StudentID CROSS APPLY (VALUES (e.GradeLevel, ts.SchoolYear4Digit, ts.TestPeriod, ts.TestSubjectGroup, #, ts.TestType, ts.TestScore) , (e.GradeLevel, pe.SchoolYear4Digit, #, #, # , #) , (e.GradeLevel, es.SchoolYear4Digit, es.Period, #, #, #, es.Score) ) x (EnrollmentGrade, SchoolYear4Digit, Period, AssessmentSubject, MetricSource, MetricName, Score) ;
